WEBVTT

00:06.580 --> 00:08.116
<i>PREVIOUSLY ON "WEEDS"...</i>

00:08.149 --> 00:10.254
THERE'S A TUNNEL.
YOU MAKE A BUST...

00:11.489 --> 00:14.128
...YOU GET GUILLERMO,
AND IT NEVER COMES BACK TO ME.

00:14.161 --> 00:15.932
I KNOW YOU'RE THE RAT.

00:15.965 --> 00:18.236
AND RATS DIE.

00:18.270 --> 00:21.042
YOU'RE THE KNOCKED‐UP
PUTA WHORE RAT.

00:21.075 --> 00:23.480
SHE END UP
IN A LANDFILL.

00:30.093 --> 00:32.064
WE SHOULD FLEE.

00:32.097 --> 00:34.703
AND I LOVE YOU.
I'm pregnant.

00:34.736 --> 00:37.441
I NEED YOU TO TAKE SHANE
UP TO MY SISTER'S
IN THE OAKLAND HILLS.

00:37.474 --> 00:40.180
JILL PRICE‐GRAY, WITH A HYPHEN?
BITCH FACE?

00:40.214 --> 00:41.550
THEY'RE AWAKE.
THEY'RE AWAKE.

00:41.584 --> 00:42.886
OH, HI.

00:42.919 --> 00:44.455
NO, YOU DESERVE
TO BE APPRECIATED,

00:44.488 --> 00:46.326
AND ME TOO, YOU KNOW,
BECAUSE, UM...

00:46.359 --> 00:50.100
IT'S JUST BEEN A LONG TIME
SINCE I WAS APPRECIATED.

00:50.133 --> 00:51.202
[ CAMERA CLICKS ]

00:51.236 --> 00:52.404
WHY ARE YOU
STILL HERE?

00:52.438 --> 00:54.242
I WILL ORGANIZE
EVERYTHING.

00:54.275 --> 00:56.580
DO NOT
MAKE ME GO BACK THERE.

00:56.614 --> 00:58.450
I HAVE NO FRIENDS.

00:58.483 --> 01:01.122
Doug: YOU GUYS OUGHT TO GROW
IN A NATIONAL PARK.

01:01.155 --> 01:03.393
ALL RIGHT, WELL,
THESE ARE MINE NOW, SILAS,

01:03.426 --> 01:04.997
NOW BOTH OF YOU
GET THE FUCK OUT OF HERE

01:05.030 --> 01:06.466
BEFORE I HAVE TO SHOOT YOU
IN THE HEAD.

01:06.499 --> 01:07.636
[ DOG BARKING ]

01:07.669 --> 01:10.040
IT'S THE DOORBELL.
HER DOORBELL BARKS?

01:10.073 --> 01:11.342
I'M HERE
TO KEEP YOU COMPANY.

01:11.376 --> 01:13.581
I DON'T NEED COMPANY.
HE THINKS YOU DO.

01:13.614 --> 01:15.417
CALL OFF YOUR GOON.

01:15.450 --> 01:18.591
YOU SHOULD BE TAKING
BETTER CARE OF MY BABY.

01:18.624 --> 01:19.392
WHAT'S THE POINT?

01:19.425 --> 01:21.697
WHEN AM I GONNA END UP
IN A LANDFILL?

01:21.730 --> 01:23.701
I HAVEN'T DECIDED.

01:24.569 --> 01:26.372
[ GASPS ]

01:26.406 --> 01:28.577
OH!

01:28.611 --> 01:32.418
YOU...DON'T DICTATE

01:32.451 --> 01:34.690
THE TERMS
OF THIS ARRANGEMENT.

01:34.723 --> 01:36.727
[ SIGHS ]

01:36.760 --> 01:38.163
TIME TO GO.

01:39.566 --> 01:41.537
[ WATER RUNNING ]

01:45.578 --> 01:47.081
[ SCRUBBING ]

02:15.571 --> 02:17.575
[ DOG BARKING ]

02:20.013 --> 02:22.251
I AM THROUGH WITH YOU.

02:22.284 --> 02:24.322
RIGHT BACK AT YOU.

02:25.424 --> 02:27.896
[ DOOR OPENS AND CLOSES ]

02:30.434 --> 02:34.408
YOU REMEMBER SUCIO.
HE WILL WATCH YOU NOW.

02:42.458 --> 02:46.399
SUCIO USUALLY TORTURES
PEOPLE FOR US.

02:46.432 --> 02:48.336
NOW HE'S THE ONE
BEING TORTURED.

02:48.370 --> 02:50.240
DON'T YOU HAVE
PEOPLE TO KILL?

02:53.380 --> 02:56.319
WOW. IS IT TOO MUCH TO ASK
THAT HE TAKES A SHOWER?

02:56.352 --> 02:59.626
HE IS COMFORTABLE
WITH HIS MAN SMELL.

02:59.659 --> 03:02.398
LIVE WITH IT.

03:10.080 --> 03:12.786
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

03:12.819 --> 03:15.625
[ ANIMALS CALLING ]

03:17.061 --> 03:19.833
WHATCHA WRITING?

03:19.866 --> 03:22.137
RANSOM NOTE.

03:22.171 --> 03:24.910
EXCITING.

03:24.943 --> 03:27.081
[ Sing‐song voice ]
RANSOM NOTE.

03:27.114 --> 03:29.318
HERE YOU GO.

03:29.351 --> 03:32.959
ARE YOU SURE
YOU SHOULDN'T TYPE THAT?

03:32.992 --> 03:34.596
THIS IS A ROUGH DRAFT.

03:34.629 --> 03:38.470
"INSISTO."

03:38.504 --> 03:39.438
OH, NO.

03:39.472 --> 03:42.144
YOU SHOULD SAY "DEMAND,"
NOT "INSIST."

03:42.177 --> 03:44.181
I MEAN, YOU DON'T
HAVE A LIST OF INSISTS.

03:44.215 --> 03:45.818
YOU HAVE
A LIST OF DEMANDS.

03:45.852 --> 03:47.054
PLEASE.

03:47.087 --> 03:50.895
I HAVE BEEN WRITING RANSOM NOTES
SINCE I WAS A VERY YOUNG BOY.

03:52.297 --> 03:54.335
WHO ARE WE KIDNAPPING?

03:54.368 --> 03:55.772
WE INTEND TO KIDNAP
THE MINISTER OF COMMERCE.

03:55.805 --> 03:59.713
HEHAS PEOPLE WHO ARE WILLING
TO PAY FOR HIS RETURN.

03:59.746 --> 04:01.349
COLD.

04:01.382 --> 04:03.486
[ EXHALES SHARPLY ]

04:03.521 --> 04:05.992
YOU KNOW, SOME PEOPLE
JUST AREN'T WRITERS.

04:06.025 --> 04:07.428
SOME PEOPLE ARE TALKERS.

04:07.461 --> 04:09.198
SO, COME ON.
LET'S TRY IT.

04:09.231 --> 04:11.804
YOU TALK,
AND I'LL JUST WRITE IT DOWN.

04:11.837 --> 04:15.477
CELIA, THANK YOU,
BUT I CAN HANDLE THIS MYSELF.

04:15.511 --> 04:19.051
PLEASE. YOU'RE A LOST PUPPY.
LET'S START AGAIN.

04:19.084 --> 04:21.523
YOU MUST STOP THIS.
STOP WHAT?

04:21.557 --> 04:23.594
I AM NOT A PUPPY.
I AM A MAN.

04:23.627 --> 04:25.698
YOU ARE UNDERMINING ME.
NO, I'M NOT.

04:29.238 --> 04:32.545
RAFAEL Y LOPEZ.
OOH...LOPEZ.

04:32.579 --> 04:36.018
NO. RAFAEL USED TO PICK ON HIM
AT SCHOOL,

04:36.052 --> 04:38.958
AND THAT DYNAMIC
STILL HASN'T CHANGED.

04:38.991 --> 04:40.360
SEND GUTIERREZ.

04:40.393 --> 04:42.699
[ PAPER RUSTLING ]

04:44.936 --> 04:47.274
I'LL JUST FINISH THIS UP.

04:48.878 --> 04:50.781
HEY.

04:54.823 --> 04:55.892
NANCE...

04:55.925 --> 04:56.960
DO I KNOW YOU?

04:56.994 --> 04:59.098
NOT FUNNY.

04:59.131 --> 05:02.739
SUCIO, BROTHER‐IN‐LAW.
NO "SHOOTIE."

05:04.843 --> 05:06.713
SUCIO, ANDY.

05:06.747 --> 05:09.018
ANDY...SUCIO.

05:09.051 --> 05:10.688
SUCIO.

05:10.721 --> 05:13.493
SU‐SU‐SUCIO?

05:13.527 --> 05:16.098
IT'S A PHIL COLLINS...

05:16.132 --> 05:18.369
HOW'D IT GO
WITH SHANE?

05:18.403 --> 05:19.573
HOW DO YOU THINK
IT WENT?

05:19.606 --> 05:22.612
HE HAD TO SLEEP IN SCOTT'S
MARATHON‐TROPHY ROOM,

05:22.645 --> 05:26.085
SHARE A BATHROOM
WITH THE CHILDREN OF THE CORN.

05:26.118 --> 05:27.522
THOSE TWINS ARE CREEPY.

05:27.555 --> 05:30.160
HE'S SAFER THERE
THAN HE IS HERE.

05:30.193 --> 05:33.934
HOW'S MY MATURE, RESPONSIBLE,
OLDER SISTER?

05:33.968 --> 05:35.705
SHE'S LOOKING HOT.

05:35.738 --> 05:37.509
SHE IS?

05:37.542 --> 05:41.550
TIME'S BEEN KIND
TO THE PRICE SISTERS.

05:41.583 --> 05:42.685
OH, DON'T LUMP US
TOGETHER.

05:42.719 --> 05:44.623
BUT YOU'RE SO ALIKE.
NO, WE'RE NOT.

05:44.656 --> 05:48.631
WE'RE NOTHING ALIKE ‐‐
NOTHING, NADA.

05:49.633 --> 05:51.870
[ SIGHS ]

05:51.904 --> 05:54.776
NO. BATHROOM. BAÑO.

05:54.809 --> 05:56.580
NO, NO. SHOO.

05:58.684 --> 06:01.455
SO, SUCIO.

06:01.489 --> 06:04.763
SUCIO...
SUCIO.

06:04.796 --> 06:07.434
REALLY, YOU'VE NEVER HEARD
THAT SONG, "SU‐SU‐SU‐‐"

06:07.467 --> 06:11.810
[ GASPS ] OKAY. WELL,
THAT CUTS OFF MY BREATHING.

06:13.213 --> 06:14.716
PAYASO.

06:14.749 --> 06:17.922
OH, I'M ‐‐ I'M A CLOWN?
IS THAT WHAT ‐‐

06:17.956 --> 06:21.730
[ TOILET FLUSHES ]
OKAY, YEAH.
I CAN LIVE WITH THAT.

06:21.763 --> 06:24.368
I HAVE TO GO
TO THE DOCTOR ‐‐ NOW.

06:24.401 --> 06:27.007
I'M BLEEDING.

06:30.848 --> 06:32.852
THIS PLACE
GIVES ME THE CREEPS.

06:32.885 --> 06:34.154
WELCOME TO MY PREGNANCY.

06:34.188 --> 06:35.625
NO ONE HERE SPEAKS ENGLISH.

06:35.658 --> 06:38.931
I'M THIRSTY AND
AFRAID TO DRINK THE WATER.

06:38.964 --> 06:41.536
THE MAGAZINES IN THE WAITING
ROOM ARE ALL IN SPANISH.

06:41.570 --> 06:44.542
I'M SORRY
THIS IS SO HARD FOR YOU.
[ DOOR OPENS ]

06:46.813 --> 06:49.619
YOU WERE BEHAVING
RECKLESSLY AGAIN.

06:49.653 --> 06:52.157
MAYBE IT'S ALL THE ROUGH SEX
I'VE BEEN HAVING.

06:52.190 --> 06:53.827
WHO IS THIS?

06:53.861 --> 06:56.767
ESTEBAN,
ANDY, MY BROTHER‐IN‐LAW.

06:56.800 --> 06:59.204
ANDY, THE FATHER
OF MY CHILD ‐‐ ESTEBAN.

06:59.238 --> 07:00.608
MM.

07:00.641 --> 07:03.012
I PICTURED YOU TALLER.

07:04.315 --> 07:06.485
HE'S NOT NEEDED HERE.

07:06.520 --> 07:08.924
OH. I THINK
SHE BEGS TO DIFFER.

07:11.697 --> 07:14.335
THAT'S YOUR CUE
TO BEGIN BEGGING TO DIFFER.

07:14.368 --> 07:15.605
[ CHUCKLES ]

07:15.638 --> 07:19.646
YOU TALK LIKE A CLOWN.
PAYASO.

07:19.679 --> 07:22.885
WHY IS THAT THE WORST THING
YOU GUYS CAN SAY TO SOMEONE?

07:23.988 --> 07:25.023
DOCTOR.

07:25.056 --> 07:27.060
BUENOS.

07:27.094 --> 07:28.931
A Mexican gyno?

07:28.964 --> 07:31.870
NANCE, IF YOU'RE PUTTING
TOGETHER A MARIACHI BAND,

07:31.903 --> 07:32.772
YES, GO MEXICAN.

07:32.805 --> 07:34.809
DOWN THERE,
YOU WANT A JEW.

07:34.843 --> 07:36.647
MM, Sí.

07:36.680 --> 07:40.153
COMO VER A CUANDO EXAMEN
POR DE MUJER EXACTAMENTE

07:40.186 --> 07:41.923
SI HAY ALGúN PROBLEMA.

07:47.334 --> 07:48.971
[ BEEPING ]

07:51.208 --> 07:53.012
HUH.

07:53.046 --> 07:55.885
vESTá BIEN, NO?

07:55.918 --> 07:57.087
vUNA PROBLEMA?

07:57.120 --> 07:59.258
NO CRAMPING?

07:59.291 --> 08:00.728
JUST SOME BLEEDING.

08:00.761 --> 08:03.667
YOU HAVE NOT INGESTED COCAINE
OR METHAMPHETAMINES, HUH?

08:03.701 --> 08:06.807
OH, I CAN ASSURE YOU
I'VE BEEN OFF COCAINE

08:06.840 --> 08:09.044
AND AMPHETAMINES
FOR ALMOST A WEEK.

08:10.280 --> 08:11.349
JOKE.

08:11.382 --> 08:13.754
[ SIGHS ]

08:26.913 --> 08:29.886
YOU'RE OKAY.
DON'T STRESS YOURSELF, HMM?

08:29.919 --> 08:32.725
I SEE YOU
FOR YOUR NEXT VISIT.

08:32.759 --> 08:35.531
GRACIAS, DOCTOR.
SEÑOR.

08:35.564 --> 08:38.302
NOW, YOU GO
STRAIGHT HOME.

08:38.336 --> 08:39.371
CAN YOU DRIVE ME?

08:39.405 --> 08:41.643
THIS LITTLE CRISIS

08:41.676 --> 08:43.981
HAS ALREADY DISRUPTED
MY SCHEDULE.

08:44.014 --> 08:45.618
NOW GO RELAX.

08:45.651 --> 08:50.293
IF I HEAR YOU'RE NOT RELAXING,
THERE WILL BE CONSEQUENCES.

08:53.767 --> 08:55.738
HEY, CONGRATULATIONS.

08:55.771 --> 08:58.042
YOU'RE GONNA BE
SUCH A GREAT DAD.

09:03.052 --> 09:05.190
PSYCH.

09:10.266 --> 09:12.839
SEE THAT ‐‐
OUTDOOR SHOWER?

09:12.872 --> 09:15.009
FEEL FREE TO USE IT
ANYTIME.

09:30.440 --> 09:32.144
NO, STAND DOWN.

09:32.177 --> 09:35.250
THAT'S MY SON ‐‐ MY SON WHO'S
SUPPOSED TO BE IN THE WOODS,

09:35.283 --> 09:36.520
TENDING TO HIS CLONES.

09:36.553 --> 09:38.824
WENT DOWN A BAD ROAD.
WHO'S THIS GUY?

09:38.857 --> 09:41.530
HE'S MY BODYGUARD ‐‐
SUCIO.

09:41.563 --> 09:43.600
OH. HOLA.

09:46.038 --> 09:47.675
Sí. HOLA.

09:47.708 --> 09:51.917
UH, YOU WANT SOME COFFEE?
BREWED A FRESH POT JUST FOR YOU.

09:54.288 --> 09:55.323
[ PATS STOMACH ]

09:55.356 --> 09:58.396
OH, PBHT! SHIT.
BABY. SORRY.

09:58.429 --> 10:01.268
YOU KNOW,
YOU DON'T LOOK IT.

10:01.302 --> 10:03.072
IN FACT, YOU LOOK GREAT.

10:03.106 --> 10:06.145
[ CHUCKLES LIGHTLY ]
GORGEOUS, THIN.

10:06.178 --> 10:07.582
HOW MUCH DO YOU NEED?

10:07.615 --> 10:09.586
[ SIGHS ]

10:10.721 --> 10:13.159
I WANT TO OPEN A STORE,

10:13.192 --> 10:17.000
A TOTALLY ABOVEBOARD
AND LEGIT RETAIL ESTABLISHMENT.

10:17.033 --> 10:20.674
WHAT EXACTLY WOULD
THIS TOTALLY ABOVEBOARD

10:20.708 --> 10:22.745
AND LEGIT RETAIL
ESTABLISHMENT SELL?

10:23.747 --> 10:25.216
MEDICAL MARIJUANA.

10:25.250 --> 10:26.385
NO.

10:26.418 --> 10:28.657
OH, COME ON!
OBAMA'S PRESIDENT.

10:28.690 --> 10:29.993
THEY'RE NOT GONNA BUST THEM
ANYMORE.

10:30.026 --> 10:32.197
YOU GOT CONTACTS
AT THE JUSTICE DEPARTMENT?

10:32.230 --> 10:33.399
IT WAS IN THE PAPER.

10:33.432 --> 10:35.671
IF IT'S LEGAL IN THE STATE,
THE FEDS WON'T COME AFTER YOU.

10:35.704 --> 10:36.940
IT'S NO‐RISK.

10:36.973 --> 10:39.178
WHERE MARIJUANA'S INVOLVED,
THERE'S ALWAYS RISK.

10:39.211 --> 10:41.850
MY EXCITING AND DEATH‐DEFYING
ADVENTURES IN THE DRUG TRADE

10:41.883 --> 10:43.119
SHOULD HAVE TAUGHT YOU THIS
BY NOW.

10:43.152 --> 10:46.058
I WILL ONLY BUY FROM GROWERS
WITH PRESCRIPTIONS.

10:46.091 --> 10:48.697
I'LL GO THROUGH ALL
THE PROPER CHANNELS, I PROMISE.

10:48.730 --> 10:50.466
I WILL DO IT RIGHT HERE
IN REN MAR.

10:50.500 --> 10:52.772
I GOT IT ALL WORKED OUT.

10:54.208 --> 10:56.045
LIKE IT OR NOT,

10:56.078 --> 10:57.915
YOU'VE MADE THIS
THE FAMILY BUSINESS.

10:57.949 --> 11:00.821
AT LEAST
I'M DOING IT LEGAL.

11:02.859 --> 11:06.198
OPENING A RETAIL STORE IS NUTS
IN THIS ECONOMY.

11:06.232 --> 11:07.167
MOM, I'M SELLING WEED.

11:07.200 --> 11:09.572
IT'S AS CLOSE TO RECESSION‐PROOF
AS IT GETS.

11:09.606 --> 11:10.875
BESIDES, DOUG IS HELPING ME.

11:10.908 --> 11:13.179
HE KNOWS ALL ABOUT
RUNNING A BUSINESS.

11:13.212 --> 11:14.047
HOW REASSURING.

11:14.081 --> 11:16.553
JUST KEEP HIM AWAY
FROM THE INVENTORY.

11:16.586 --> 11:18.122
GUINEO, GUINEO.

11:18.155 --> 11:19.291
WHOA.
IS THAT A YES?

11:20.594 --> 11:22.063
I MEAN IT, SILAS.

11:22.097 --> 11:24.067
DON'T LET DOUG
ANYWHERE NEAR THE PRODUCT.

11:24.101 --> 11:25.771
[ EXHALES DEEPLY ]

11:28.644 --> 11:30.814
OH, STOP ‐‐
OTHER SON...

11:30.848 --> 11:33.019
WHO'S SUPPOSED TO BE IN OAKLAND
WITH MY SISTER.

11:33.052 --> 11:36.392
WHAT THE HELL
ARE YOU DOING HERE?
I'M DONE.

11:36.425 --> 11:38.396
SUCIO, THAT'S MY SISTER.

11:38.429 --> 11:40.233
YOU CAN SHOOT HER
IF YOU WANT.

11:41.235 --> 11:42.270
NOT REALLY.

11:42.304 --> 11:43.974
SHE BANGED UNCLE ANDY.

11:44.007 --> 11:45.176
YOU DIDN'T.

11:45.210 --> 11:47.180
WHAT?
I CAN DO THINGS.

11:47.214 --> 11:49.351
OH, MY GOD.

11:49.384 --> 11:52.725
SHE'S A SCREAMER.
WOULD YOU SHUT UP,
YOU WEIRD LITTLE PERVERT?

11:52.758 --> 11:56.232
HE WAS TAKING PICTURES
AND WAS GONNA SHOW SCOTT.

11:56.265 --> 11:57.902
OH, GOOD MOVE.

11:57.935 --> 12:00.941
SHANE, YOU'RE GOING BACK
WITH AUNT JILL.

12:00.975 --> 12:03.714
YOU WILL KEEP YOUR MOUTH SHUT
TO HER HUSBAND AND HER CHILDREN

12:03.747 --> 12:05.718
ABOUT WHAT A NASTY WHORE
THEIR MOMMY IS.

12:05.751 --> 12:06.886
IS THAT CLEAR?

12:06.920 --> 12:10.794
OH, NO, HE'S ALL YOURS ‐‐
IN SO MANY WAYS.

12:10.828 --> 12:12.632
CAN I GO UPSTAIRS
AND UNPACK?

12:12.665 --> 12:13.967
YES.
NO.

12:18.777 --> 12:21.983
BYE, AUNT JILL.
[ FOOTSTEPS ASCENDING STAIRS ]

12:22.017 --> 12:25.925
YOUR LITTLE MONSTER
IS NOT COMING BACK TO MY HOME.

12:25.958 --> 12:27.360
THE PERFECT
JILL PRICE‐GRAY,

12:27.394 --> 12:29.298
WITH HER PERFECT HUSBAND
AND HER PERFECT HOUSE,

12:29.331 --> 12:32.571
CAN'T DO THE ONLY THING I'VE
EVER ASKED HER IN MY WHOLE LIFE.

12:32.605 --> 12:34.074
OH, YOU'RE JOKING.

12:34.107 --> 12:36.378
EVERY SENTENCE OUT OF YOUR MOUTH
STARTS WITH,

12:36.412 --> 12:38.650
"OH, JILL, WOULD YOU,
COULD YOU, DO YOU MIND IF..."

12:38.684 --> 12:40.219
WHY DO YOU THINK
I STOPPED TALKING TO YOU?

12:40.253 --> 12:42.023
'CAUSE YOU'RE
A SELF‐RIGHTEOUS BITCH.

12:42.057 --> 12:44.595
YOU KNOW WHAT?
I DON'T NEED THIS.

12:44.629 --> 12:46.700
I'M BETTER.
THIS WAS A SLIP.

12:46.733 --> 12:48.269
I'VE WORKED THROUGH
MY CODEPENDENCE,

12:48.302 --> 12:50.306
AND I'M DONE BAILING YOU OUT
EVERY TIME YOU GET INTO TROUBLE.

12:50.340 --> 12:52.945
YOU DON'T BAIL ME OUT.
YOU JUST LECTURE.

12:52.979 --> 12:54.649
THAT'S A CUTE NECKLACE.

12:54.682 --> 12:56.987
THEN I'LL SPARE YOU
THE LECTURE.

12:57.020 --> 12:59.091
I GOT IT AT NORDSTROM.
OH, NO, YOU KNOW WHAT?

12:59.124 --> 13:00.894
I THINK I GOT THIS ONLINE
AT ETSY.

13:00.928 --> 13:01.997
OH.

13:03.533 --> 13:08.409
PLEASE...
DO ME THIS ONE FAVOR.

13:08.442 --> 13:10.013
SHANE'S NOT SAFE HERE.

13:10.046 --> 13:12.685
ARE YOU OKAY?
I'M FINE.

13:12.718 --> 13:16.358
NOTHING.
I'M JUST...PREGNANT.

13:16.392 --> 13:17.962
WHO'S THE FATHER?

13:17.995 --> 13:19.532
IT'S COMPLICATED.

13:19.565 --> 13:20.734
YEAH, WELL, IT ALWAYS IS
WITH YOU.

13:20.768 --> 13:21.870
YOU KNOW WHAT, JILL?

13:21.903 --> 13:24.207
IF YOU'RE NOT GONNA HELP ME,
THEN FUCK OFF.

13:27.515 --> 13:30.320
IS ‐‐
Is he the father?

13:30.353 --> 13:31.623
SURE.

13:31.656 --> 13:33.727
YOU REALLY WILL SLEEP
WITH ANYTHING.

13:33.760 --> 13:37.200
LOOK WHO'S TALKING.
Andy: WE HAVE
ELECTRICAL TAPE, RIGHT?

13:38.870 --> 13:40.808
JILL, WHAT ARE YOU
DOING HERE?

13:40.841 --> 13:42.310
Asshole.

13:49.458 --> 13:51.362
COME ON, NANCE.
IS IT SO OUT OF CHARACTER?

13:51.395 --> 13:55.904
LET'S GET OUT OF HERE.
DO YOU LIVE NEAR HERE?

13:55.938 --> 13:58.009
UPSTAIRS.
REALLY?

13:58.042 --> 14:01.315
EH, OKAY,
LET'S GO UPSTAIRS.

14:01.348 --> 14:02.885
[ CLICKS TONGUE ]

14:04.889 --> 14:07.360
[ FOOTSTEPS ASCEND STAIRS ]

14:24.094 --> 14:28.069
OKAY, EVERYTHING
SEEMS TO BE IN ORDER HERE ‐‐

14:28.102 --> 14:30.173
SOCIAL SECURITY NUMBERS.

14:30.206 --> 14:31.375
UH, WAIT. WAIT.

14:31.408 --> 14:35.183
WHERE IT SAYS, "STATE FULLY
THE EXACT NATURE OF BUSINESS

14:35.216 --> 14:36.820
FOR WHICH
A LICENSE IS REQUIRED,"

