15:21.375 --> 15:24.014
JACKPOT!

15:24.047 --> 15:25.818
SOUR PUNCH BITES.

15:25.851 --> 15:27.320
WE SHOULD LEAVE.

15:27.353 --> 15:29.191
LOOK, I AM VERY HIGH,
AND I'M NOT PARANOID.

15:29.224 --> 15:32.263
SO YOU, BEING NOT HIGH, SHOULD
BE EVEN MORE NOT PARANOID.

15:32.297 --> 15:35.303
UNLESS YOU ARE HIGH.
ARE YOU HIGH?

15:35.336 --> 15:36.472
YOU'RE RIGHT.

15:36.506 --> 15:39.579
WHAT WE'RE DOING HERE
IS PERFECTLY LEGAL.
PERFECTLY.

15:39.612 --> 15:41.348
I'VE GOT NOTHING
TO BE AFRAID OF.

15:41.381 --> 15:43.587
NOTHING.

15:43.620 --> 15:45.624
EXCEPT MAYBE THAT GUY.

15:47.093 --> 15:49.866
GENTLEMEN, I'M AFRAID WE
CAN'T APPROVE YOUR APPLICATION

15:49.899 --> 15:51.803
WITHOUT THE SIGNED,
AUTHORIZED CONSENT

15:51.836 --> 15:53.640
OF A LOCAL
LAW‐ENFORCEMENT OFFICIAL.

15:53.673 --> 15:56.646
LAW ENFORCEMENT?
OH, GREAT.

15:56.679 --> 15:58.048
SOUR PUNCH BITES?

15:58.082 --> 16:00.721
OH, NO, THANK YOU.
I HAVE SOME OF MY OWN.

16:04.327 --> 16:05.296
[ SIGHS ]

16:05.329 --> 16:07.768
OKAY, WAIT. WAIT.
LET ME THINK.

16:07.802 --> 16:10.273
OH, YES,
I HAVE A GOOD ONE.

16:10.306 --> 16:11.943
I DON'T THINK
I LIKE THIS GAME.

16:11.976 --> 16:13.412
KEEP GOING.

16:13.445 --> 16:15.416
