THAT'S TOTAL BULLSHIT.

16:22.565 --> 16:25.136
OH. BET SHE WAS A REAL
HEARTBREAKER IN JUNIOR HIGH ‐‐

16:25.169 --> 16:27.508
BODY FULLY DEVELOPED,
PRECOCIOUS, SOPHISTICATED,

16:27.541 --> 16:30.413
BORED WITH ALL
THE OTHER KIDS HER AGE.

16:30.446 --> 16:33.419
MM, NOT REALLY ‐‐
FLAT, CLIQUEY, "B" AVERAGE.

16:33.452 --> 16:35.223
FIRST, MORE WINE?

16:35.256 --> 16:39.030
THIS WHOLE NOT‐DRINKING
THING SUCKS.
MORE FOR US.

16:39.064 --> 16:41.001
ANYWAY...

16:41.034 --> 16:43.974
HIS NAME WAS MR. SCHIFF,

16:44.007 --> 16:46.913
