17:03.647 --> 17:06.151
HE USED TO SEND YOU NOTES
FROM THE LOONY BIN.

17:06.184 --> 17:09.024
W‐WHY IS THIS
YOUR FAVORITE STORY?
BECAUSE IT'S AWESOME.

17:09.057 --> 17:10.761
