17:29.932 --> 17:33.339
THAN HE WAS TO YOU.
YOU ARE STILL
JUST A RAGING NARCISSIST.

17:33.372 --> 17:35.777
I DON'T EVEN KNOW
WHY WE'RE ARGUING ABOUT THIS.

17:35.811 --> 17:37.247
I WAS 13.
THE MAN WAS A PEDOPHILE.

17:37.280 --> 17:39.417
LADIES, PLEASE,
