[ SIGHS ]

17:58.957 --> 18:01.495
[ INSECTS CHIRPING ]

18:06.038 --> 18:07.206
[ GASPS ]

18:07.240 --> 18:09.444
[ MUFFLED SCREAMING ]

18:10.781 --> 18:12.851
SO, A‐AM I
HEARING THIS RIGHT?

18:12.885 --> 18:17.360
NEXT TO MOLLY'S PET DEPOT, WHERE
I GOT MY FIRST DOG, SCRAGGLES,

18:17.393 --> 18:20.132
ACROSS FROM
THE SURFSIDE PANCAKE HUT...

18:20.166 --> 18:23.339
YOU GUYS
