EXACTLY.

18:23.372 --> 18:25.109
UH, FOR MEDICAL PURPOSES
ONLY,

18:25.142 --> 18:27.046
STRICTLY
COMPASSIONATE CARE.

18:27.080 --> 18:29.719
BOYS, THIS IS
A WHOLESOME TOWN.

18:29.752 --> 18:32.457
I GREW UP HERE,
LIVED MY WHOLE LIFE HERE.

18:32.490 --> 18:34.962
