18:34.996 --> 18:38.168
SO, UH...

18:38.202 --> 18:41.274
I'M GONNA WANT MY CUT.

18:41.308 --> 18:42.343
CUT?

18:42.377 --> 18:44.582
FIXED MONTHLY PAYMENT
OR PERCENTAGE OF THE SALES ‐‐

18:44.615 --> 18:46.251
YOUR CHOICE.

18:47.387 --> 18:49.391
Doug:
CAN WE HAVE A SECOND?

18:49.424 --> 18:51.763
