YOU'RE GONNA LOVE IT.

20:36.037 --> 20:38.041
OKAY.

20:38.075 --> 20:40.580
UM...SOAP.

20:40.614 --> 20:42.718
JABóN. SOAP.

20:42.751 --> 20:44.655
UH, SHAMPOO.

20:44.688 --> 20:46.926
