THE WORD FOR THAT, EITHER.

20:53.405 --> 20:57.246
LAVAR.
LAVAR. vSí?

20:57.280 --> 21:01.923
COMO SE LLAMA...
"LOOFAH"?

21:01.956 --> 21:04.595
Loofah.

21:04.628 --> 21:06.264
Right.

21:08.603 --> 21:12.578
I'M JUST GONNA GO GET
YOUR LOOFAH, OKAY? UNO MINUTO.

21:18.823 --> 21:20.326
Jill: OH!
Andy: OH, GOD.

21:20.359 --> 21:21.629
YOU'RE GONNA MISS
YOUR FLIGHT, BABY.

21:21.662 --> 21:23.566
OH, I DON'T CARE.
IT'S OKAY. I DON'T CARE.

21:23.600 --> 21:24.902
I DON'T CARE.
SCREW THE FLIGHT.

21:24.935 --> 21:26.973
THIS MIGHT BE THE LAST TIME
I COME BY FUCKING.

21:27.006 --> 21:28.943
ALL RIGHT.
I'M WORKING ON IT.

21:28.977 --> 21:30.614
Shh.

21:30.647 --> 21:33.820
ALL RIGHT. COME ON.
[ CHUCKLES ]

21:33.853 --> 21:38.563
OH, GOD. THAT'S IT.
THAT'S IT. YEAH.

21:38.596 --> 21:41.034
OH.
FUCKING SHIT!
[ GLASS BREAKS ]

21:41.067 --> 21:42.871
[ BANGING, MOANING ]

21:42.905 --> 21:44.508
[ Chuckling ]
OH, MAN.

21:44.542 --> 21:47.079
THAT'S IT.
I GOT A LITTLE MORE.

21:47.113 --> 21:48.683
[ WATER RUNNING ]

21:48.716 --> 21:51.321
SUCIO? SUCIO?

21:51.354 --> 21:55.296
I KNOW YOU'RE NAKED ‐‐
MAYBE EVEN CLEAN.

21:55.329 --> 21:58.503
I KNOW IT'S VERY SCARY FOR YOU.
AND NEW.

21:58.536 --> 22:02.043
SUCIO?
DóNDE ESTá USTED?

22:12.564 --> 22:16.137
SHANE...
HAVE YOU SEEN SUCIO?

22:16.171 --> 22:17.473
NO.

22:17.508 --> 22:20.412
