NOW HE'S GONE.

22:20.446 --> 22:22.885
[ GROANS LIGHTLY ]
COME ON, SHANE.

22:22.918 --> 22:25.256
HERE WE GO.

22:25.289 --> 22:27.059
COVER YOUR EARS.

22:27.093 --> 22:30.734
STAY WHERE I CAN SEE YOU
