WANT TO KNOW WHAT'S GOING ON?

24:15.242 --> 24:18.315
I HAVE FUCKED UP MY ENTIRE LIFE
IN WAYS YOU CAN'T EVEN IMAGINE,

24:18.348 --> 24:21.589
AND I DON'T THINK I'M GONNA BE
ABLE TO GET OUT OF IT THIS TIME.

24:21.622 --> 24:23.926
AND WHAT AM I SUPPOSED TO DO
WITH THAT?

24:23.960 --> 24:25.630
GET ON A PLANE.
GO BACK TO YOUR FAMILY.

24:25.664 --> 24:26.799
BE GLAD YOU'RE NOT ME.

24:26.832 --> 24:29.705
SORRY, BUT I
WOULD FUCKING LOVE TO BE YOU.

24:29.738 --> 24:33.045
GETTING KIND OF STUFFY
IN THERE.
GET BACK IN THE CAR.

24:33.078 --> 24:34.414
OH, YOU'RE FIGHTING.

24:34.447 --> 24:36.151
Both:
BACK IN THE CAR!

24:37.554 --> 24:39.758
YOU JUST TOOK OFF
AND PUT IT ALL ON ME.

24:39.792 --> 24:41.762
[ SIGHS ]

24:41.796 --> 24:43.933
I WAS A KID.
YOU WERE OLDER.

24:43.966 --> 24:46.338
BY A YEAR AND A HALF.

24:46.371 --> 24:47.641
I COULDN'T HANDLE IT,
OKAY?

24:47.674 --> 24:50.446
WELL, GUESS FUCKING WHAT ‐‐
