'DO NOT RESUSCITATE' ORDERS."

25:18.068 --> 25:20.507
ALL RIGHT.

25:20.540 --> 25:21.809
I'M SORRY.

25:21.842 --> 25:26.652
I'M SORRY I AM ‐‐ HAVE BEEN ‐‐
SUCH A DISAPPOINTMENT.

25:26.685 --> 25:30.994
I REALIZE THAT'S
A LOT TO HANG ON TO, AND...

25:31.027 --> 25:32.196
IT MUST REALLY SUCK.

25:32.229 --> 25:35.970
NOW, WILL YOU PLEASE
GET IN THE FUCKING CAR?

25:36.004 --> 25:37.006
